name: TinFoilChef TCG Card
description:
TinFoilChef, also written as Tinfoil Chef or abbreviated as TFC, was a YouTuber and member of Hermitcraft. He joined in Season 2 and was an active member up until his death on August 13, 2022. He has 124,000 subscribers. His most viewed video is Hermitcraft 9 Ep4.

The card is based of a card from the Hermitcraft Trading Card Game (TCG), a server-wide minigame in HermitCraft Season 9 created by VintageBeef.
